{"type": "article", "id": 49465, "title": "Céline 新任创意总监来自 YSL，以及，Vetements走秀去了古董市场 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-01-22T03:47:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 46129, "name": "Maison Kitsune"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 12231, "name": "Sacai"}, {"id": 45529, "name": "Vetements"}, {"id": 906, "name": "川久保玲"}, {"id": 47238, "name": "Highsnobiety"}, {"id": 1922, "name": "Celine"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180122112910ixys9jzA8IQPHrlG.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/exclusive-hedi-slimane-joins-celine-lvmh-add-menswear-11116665/?curator=FashionREDEF\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Hedi Slimane 将加入 Céline 成为其创意总监，并将扩展男装业务</strong></a> | 日前，LVMH 集团发布声明称，Hedi Slimane 将在 2 月 1 日接替 Phoebe Philo，担任 Céline 的艺术、创意及形象总监。Hedi Slimane 于 1997 加入 YSL 并迅速晋升为创意总监，2000 年转投 Dior，2012 年又再次返回 YSL，并于 2016 年离开。据称，Hedi Slimane 上任之后将致力于为 Céline 扩展男装业务。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/media/highsnobiety-secures-8-5-million-investment-11110306/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>潮流生活方式网站 Highsnobiety 获得 850 万美元融资</strong></a> | Highsnobiety 接受了一笔 850 万美元的融资，投资方为 Felix Capital。这是 Highsnobiety 自 2005 年成立以来第一次接受外部融资，新投资将用于拓展内容板块 Highsnobiety+ 以及即将推出的一系列线下活动。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/chanel-ss18-sports-accessories-buy/#slide-4\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chanel 即将上架一个奢侈的生活方式配件系列</a>。包括售价 1773 美元的网球拍，21891 美元的冲浪板，7203 美元的瑜伽垫和 9649 美元的坐垫。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122111946Y8Mp19mASWUPzsCv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122111946RktmPnWf3phl4szv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122111940B7GKAotFz5DRpeOQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122111940FOCaRYyM1drHsfD8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/vetements-fw18/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Vetements</a> 2018 秋冬系列来到了巴黎的一个古董市场，其中一套 look 中，Demna Gvasalia 让模特穿上了手绘“大象在房间”的 T 恤，说是致敬曾对他影响深远的 Maison Margiela。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112024o7WeNwtzuvFIBSl4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112027tSQ1qjRONl85gmkz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112028aZ5nv9DbzcOuARLt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112029dXDkKTC80ewfxZ5R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112031x5QvumBY1PSy2R6C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112031Is9tUSROgZNvBhVX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801221120329uYlRye2hGXWZdLO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112034dZ3CIxkjRSo9fnls.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112035IN7VQzDHAKrCYEhg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801221120362SANYTfc70h3x1wi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112036IywVbPM1hTBeamtd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112037qlkHt7xBDgML1U4N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112038koDNPtuq5SmnrHic.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112041a9KpojMrE3mFTBfb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>有着法国和日本基因的品牌<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/539358\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Maison Kitsune</a>，发布了 2018 秋冬男装系列，还不错。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112136u3rtdc0lLEgIo7qO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498536\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112146yvikG4OXa3M2gU6d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.486091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112146wzTxph7ok9BIv6n5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801221121477hODzjILTWNJ8U3P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498536\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112148HizwpcqvnL4VrDCK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498536\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112203tW3cfaelpqATygoC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.486091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112205FEjtmBnwD79qMxil.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.486091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112206ld9TKSEDbyCu2G0k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498536\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0p