 data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>川久保玲在 1984 年创立的男装支线 <a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/540474\" rel=\"nofollow\">COMME DES GARCONS HOMME PLUS</a>，向来以自由先锋的风格著称。这次的巴黎秀场上，品牌让模特戴上了怪物头套走秀，效果有点惊悚... </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112316lBnXKbGrimvjTzsJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112318UWG7vfn0upSTwI1P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112318E6TXQD4e2yRVLWZU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801221123197NMb2pguA4ynXxtj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112318KRDuChMAg9ev3lck.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112336LSiWAhy9rKxvqpGP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112337dJpjSc3xoiNqlTDC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112337DsFO7Cdc32fMaWle.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112337rhsZt7EBSPIoy6M8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112337rU8cZTgEny0JpDOH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112329i2elMCm0x5Aync8d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180122112339vDoLUKs9ypaHeOGq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\